Qatar to Name World Cup Consultant in November, Independent Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-10-16T12:25:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/qatar-to-name-world-cup-consultant-in-november-independent-says.html
Qatar will announce next month the
group to oversee the construction of facilities for the 2022
soccer World Cup, the Independent on Sunday  reported , without
saying where it got the information.  Arup Ltd., a U.K. consulting company, is bidding with CH2M
Hill Cos., according to the newspaper. Other bidders include  KBR
Inc. (KBR) , Turner International and  Aecom Technology Corp. (ACM) , the
Independent on Sunday said. Mace, the company involved in the
construction of a London skyscraper known as the Shard, has also
expressed interest in the work, the report said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Rachel Graham in London at 
 rgraham13@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Harrison at 
 mharrison5@bloomberg.net  